    com.ericelsken.android.web  

    • Uses of ExceptionHandler in com.ericelsken.android.web

      Classes in com.ericelsken.android.web that implement ExceptionHandler 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  DefaultExceptionHandler
      This class is a simple implementation of ExceptionHandler that simply logs an Exception and returns false to indicate that the Exception was not handled, allowing for other parts of this library to handle the Exception.
      Methods in com.ericelsken.android.web that return ExceptionHandler 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ExceptionHandler RequestHandler.getExceptionHandler()
      Returns the ExceptionHandler currently being used by this handler.
      ExceptionHandler RequestManager.getExceptionHandler()
      Returns the current default ExceptionHandler.
      Methods in com.ericelsken.android.web with parameters of type ExceptionHandler 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void RequestHandler.setExceptionHandler(ExceptionHandler handler)
      Sets the ExceptionHandler that will be called on future events in the Request life-cycle.
      void RequestManager.setExceptionHandler(ExceptionHandler handler)
      Sets the ExceptionHandler that will be used by all RequestHandlers created after this call returns.
